race.comment: RUM RUMBLE (5) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Can run a big race while fresh. HAPHAZARD (12) shed the maiden tag at the latest outing and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Can go right on with the job now. ALL TOO VEGAS (7) has a handy record over this sprint journey with a win and three seconds from seven attempts. Gets 3kg weight relief with the claim and rates a genuine top-three candidate. HOLD MY HALO (16) boasts a win and three seconds from ten spins around this circuit and looks one for the multiples. CUP OF AMBITION (11) has won her past two, albeit in lesser grade, and shouldn't be underestimated.
